			<p class="caption"><em>Discover more without missing out</em></p>
			<p class="caption">During research we learned that although streaming apps have risen in popularity, they still lack some of the benefits people enjoy from cable T.V. experiences. Mostly the ability to just put something on and browse through a T.V. guide. With this in mind, we designed and built a browsing drawer that let users browse options without having to leave the video player.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
