						<h2>User Testing</h2>
						<p class="last-graf">We tested two major concepts for the core video player interaction: Immersive Video Player (the video player takes over the entire screen and the users can browse content through a contextual drawer) VS. In-Page Video Player (the video player is a part of a larger page of content--users must scroll down to explore more content). The Results showed a larger preference for the Immersive Video Player. We used the testing to validate our design choice and ultimately went with the immersive experience.</p>
